# 2026-06-06 16:39:50.479225
+Loyihaga jonli efir (Kamera/Mikrofon) va real-vaqtda ishlaydigan jonli chat funksiyasini qo'shishimiz kerak. Buning uchun quyidagi ishlarni amalga oshir:
+
+1. YANGL KUTUBXONALAR:
+   - `requirements.txt` fayliga `channels` va `channels-redis` (WebSocket uchun) kutubxonalarini qo'sh.
+
+2. SOZLAMALAR (`mini_hemis/settings.py` va `complete_settings.py`):
+   - `INSTALLED_APPS` ichiga 'channels' ni qo'sh.
+   - ASGI server sozlamasini (`ASGI_APPLICATION = 'mini_hemis.asgi.application'`) sozla.
+   - Quyidagicha vaqtinchalik xotira (In-Memory) Channel Layer sozlamasini qo'sh (Redis hozircha shart bo'lmasligi uchun):
+     CHANNEL_LAYERS = {
+         "default": {
+             "BACKEND": "channels.layers.InMemoryChannelLayer",
+         },
+     }
+
+3. CHAT LOGIKASI (WebSockets):
+   - `core/consumers.py` faylini yarat va u yerda `AsyncWebsocketConsumer` orqali guruhli chat xabarlarini qabul qiladigan va barcha tomoshabinlarga tarqatadigan xonalar (Room) logikasini yoz.
+   - `core/routing.py` faylini yaratib, websocket yo'nalishini (`ws/live/<room_name>/`) ula.
+   - Proyekt ildizidagi `asgi.py` faylini yangilab, `ProtocolTypeRouter` orqali HTTP va URLRouter (WebSockets) ni ajratib ber.
+
+4. VIEW VA SHABLON (UI):
+   - `core/views.py` ichiga `live_stream(request, room_name)` funksiyasini qo'sh.
+   - `templates/live_stream.html` shablonini yarat. Shablon ichida:
+     - Chap tomonda: `<video id="localVideo" autoplay playsinline muted></video>` tegi bo'lsin. JavaScript orqali `navigator.mediaDevices.getUserMedia({video: true, audio: true})` yordamida kamerani yoqib, videoga uzatish kodini yoz.
+     - O'ng tomonda: Jonli chat oynasi (xabarlar chiqadigan joy, matn kiritish inputi va "Yuborish" tugmasi) bo'lsin. JavaScript `new WebSocket()` orqali chatga ulansin va xabarlarni real-vaqtda ekranga chiqarsin.
+
+5. URL YO'NALISHLARI:
+   - `core/urls.py` ichiga `path('live/<str:room_name>/', views.live_stream, name='live_stream')` marshrutini qo'sh.
+
+Hamma SEARCH/REPLACE bloklarini va yangi fayllarni to'liq tayyorlab ber.

