+Loyiha marshrutlarida va jonli efir shablonida jiddiy xatolik bor, shuni uzil-kesil tuzatishimiz kerak. Quyidagi o'zgarishlarni kirit:
+
+1. BACKEND ROUTINGNI TO'G'RILASH (`core/routing.py`):
+   - URL marshrutini oxirida slash bo'lgan va bo'lmagan har qanday holatga mos keladigan qilib ikkala variantini ham yoz yoki xavfsiz holatga keltir:
+     from django.urls import re_path
+     from . import consumers
+
+     websocket_urlpatterns = [
+         re_path(r'^ws/live/(?[a-zA-Z0-9_-]+)/?$', consumers.ChatConsumer.as_abstract_class() if hasattr(consumers.ChatConsumer, 'as_abstract_class') else consumers.ChatConsumer.as_asgi()),
+     ]
+
+2. SHABLONDAGI WEBSOCKET MANZILINI VA RUXSATLARNI YANGILASH (`templates/live_stream.html`):
+   - JavaScript ichidagi `ws_path` yaratilishini to'g'rilash:
+     const roomName = "{{ room_name }}";
+     const ws_scheme = window.location.protocol === "https:" ? "wws" : "ws";
+     // URL oxirida ortiqcha slash muammosini yo'qotish uchun aniq format:
+     const chatSocket = new WebSocket(ws_scheme + '://' + window.location.host + '/ws/live/' + roomName);
+
+3. SUPER ADMIN LOGIKASI (ZOOM TIZIMI):
+   - Faqat `{% if request.user.is_superuser %}` ichida Admin boshqaruv paneli ("Efirni boshlash", "Ekranni ulash", "Efirni yakunlash") ko'rinsin. Admin kamerani yoki ekranni ulash tugmasini bosgandagina WebRTC jarayoni boshlansin.
+   - Oddiy foydalanuvchilar (talaba/operator) maxsus havola bilan kirganda ulardan kamera/mikrofon ruxsati so'ralmasin, faqat `<video id="remoteVideo">` orqali admin uzatayotgan efir (kamera yoki ekran) va chat oynasi real-vaqtda ko'rinsin.
+   - Chatda kim yozsa ham (`chat_message`) barcha qatnashchilar ekranida xabarlar sekundiga yetmasdan paydo bo'lsin.
+
+Hamma SEARCH/REPLACE bloklarini chiroyli va xatosiz qo'lla.

