# 2026-06-08 12:20:10.029674
+Lokal tarmoqda (10.42.0.251 va 10.42.0.21) WebRTC oqimi bir-biriga 100% yetib borishi uchun `templates/live_stream.html` ichidagi JavaScript kodini quyidagicha yangila:
+
+1. ICE CANDIDATE HIYLASI (mDNS bypass):
+   - `peerConnection.onicecandidate` funksiyasini top. Agar `event.candidate` mavjud bo'lsa va uning ichida mDNS (ya'ni `.local` bilan tugaydigan yashirin nom) bo'lsa, uni bizning qat'iy lokal IP manzilimizga almashtiradigan yoki to'g'ridan-to'g'ri lokal tarmoq uchun signal yuboradigan mantiq qo'sh:
+
+```javascript
+peerConnection.onicecandidate = event => {
+    if (event.candidate) {
+        let candidateStr = event.candidate.candidate;
+        // Agar brauzer lokal IP'ni yashirgan bo'lsa, uni majburiy ravishda server IP'siga yo'naltiramiz
+        if (candidateStr.includes(".local")) {
+            console.log("mDNS aniqlandi, lokal IP majburlanmoqda...");
+        }
+        safeSend({
+            'type': 'candidate',
+            'candidate': event.candidate
+        });
+    }
+};

